==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flea-bite
<hw>Flea"-bite`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
bite of a flea, or the red spot caused by the bite.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A trifling wound or pain, like that of the bite of a
flea.</def> <rj><au>Harvey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>flea-bitten</ent>⟦br⟧
